00:16:45.000 --> 00:16:49.892
and all these things I just can’t understand. God has created no sects, nothing.

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:55.892
He has only created two types of human beings, one who are realized, one who are not.

00:16:56.000 --> 00:17:01.892
