00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:08.892
at that point where you can say those who are not realized. But I can’t think of any other thing, I mean,

00:17:09.000 --> 00:17:14.892
God has created different type of faces, for example somebody has, say, blond hair,

00:17:15.000 --> 00:17:18.892
somebody has black hair, somebody has white skin, black skin…

00:17:19.000 --> 00:17:24.892
He had to do like that, otherwise we would all have looked like machines, like these chairs that are here,

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:30.892
we would have had no beauty about us, isn’t it? There would have been no variety,

00:17:31.000 --> 00:17:34.892
such a boring thing to see, all these chairs morning till evening.

00:17:35.000 --> 00:17:41.892
That’s why He created this beauty, He made us so beautiful, by giving us different permutations and combinations,

00:17:42.000 --> 00:17:49.892
and things, it’s such a, such a work He has put in, while we are trying to become machine-like bolts and nuts

00:17:50.000 --> 00:17:58.892
and we become sort of, as they call it the “work”, you see, the work we become of God. Which is absurd.

00:17:59.000 --> 00:18:04.892
Say, in the nature if you see, even one leaf is not just the same like the other leaf.

00:18:05.000 --> 00:18:12.892
Even there. Variety creates the beauty. And all these points, also people are there,

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:19.892
there might be leagues here for the red hair league, and the black hair league, or maybe any sort of a,

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:26.892
any nonsensical thing they can use it, you can’t say what, to what extent they can go in forming a club

00:18:27.000 --> 00:18:33.892
