00:18:34.000 --> 00:18:37.892
Whether you have a black skin or a white skin, whether you have a bald head or a red head,

00:18:38.000 --> 00:18:43.892
you all have this thing inside you. All of you have got this universal thing within you,

00:18:44.000 --> 00:18:49.892
except for the devils. If you are a human being you all have this thing within you.

