01:21:19.000 --> 01:21:22.892
Seeker: And some even in the center? Warren repeats: And some in the center?

01:21:23.000 --> 01:21:26.892
Seeker: Is there a karmic patent or…? Warren: Is there a karmic patent, he says?

01:21:27.000 --> 01:21:31.892
Shri Mataji: There is, you see, we are made of three gunas.

01:21:32.000 --> 01:21:35.892
