01:21:36.000 --> 01:21:45.892
And those who are tamo gunis, more desires they have, the more sort of emotional they are, they are on the left side.

01:21:46.000 --> 01:21:51.892
Those who are ambitious, are on the right side. And those who are wiser are in the center.

01:21:52.000 --> 01:21:56.892
So it’s a temperament with which you are born. It has many reasons. It’s the background,

01:21:57.000 --> 01:22:05.892
it’s the things you have come out of it, and what was your education, how were your parents – I mean,

01:22:06.000 --> 01:22:12.892
so many things work it out, the personality. And these three gunas, tamo, rajo and sattwa gunas,

01:22:13.000 --> 01:22:18.892
these three qualities within us, work out permutations and combinations of all the people.

01:22:19.000 --> 01:22:26.892
And that’s how we have different type of people. And according to their style they move to one side or another.

01:22:27.000 --> 01:22:40.892
Alright? I will be talking about that also maybe if I have time, about tamo guna, rajo guna and sattwa guna.

