01:26:06.000 --> 01:26:10.892
We have some other people also, who may be coming and going from Philadelphia,

01:26:11.000 --> 01:26:20.892
and you people could be here – I’ll also come back again if you call Me. Next year maybe. We all can go to India also.

01:26:21.000 --> 01:26:28.892
We are going to go to India…when? (Warren: “In…” Shri Mataji: “Eh?” Warren: “… December”) December.

01:26:29.000 --> 01:26:34.892
If you people want to come to India, we can take you down to India also, in December;

01:26:35.000 --> 01:26:40.892
and we will have a program of about – how many days? Warren: About forty-five – fifty days.

01:26:41.000 --> 01:26:43.892
Shri Mataji: About of forty-five – fifty days, we’ll be passing through villages and all that,

01:26:44.000 --> 01:26:50.892
and that’s you mix up with other people, and learn about Sahaj Yog, is a very good way of learning about Sahaj Yog, you see,

01:26:51.000 --> 01:26:56.892
where you learn how to give Realization, and imbibe things, and it’s very good way.

01:26:57.000 --> 01:27:04.892
If you want you can come along and it is going to be quite cheap for you, only you have to pay for your food and for your travelling,

01:27:05.000 --> 01:27:10.892
that’s all, and food will be very cheaply arranged; and very good food, we can arrange that.

01:27:11.000 --> 01:27:17.892
And this time – last time they paid three pounds per day, this time they are going to pay four pounds per day.

01:27:18.000 --> 01:27:26.892
And everything can be done, we’ll go to different villages, and stay there and organize it.

01:27:27.000 --> 01:27:36.892
It’s not going to be any money-making proposition or anything, it’s a thing by which you go into simpler places and learn about Sahaj Yog.

01:27:37.000 --> 01:27:46.892
It’s better, because here, you see, it’s very quiet in this place, I feel, but otherwise in New York you have such a horrible, this signaling business, you know?

01:27:47.000 --> 01:27:55.892
And all the sounds – and the atmosphere is so much filled with funny sounds all over, and it’s horrifying.

01:27:56.000 --> 01:28:00.892
Warren: Mother, a lot of people have asked about the practices, how they learn the practices for Sahaja Yoga,

01:28:01.000 --> 01:28:08.892
the various things they can do, that they have to do. And I think they should all know that you just come along to the group,

01:28:09.000 --> 01:28:14.892
after Mother’s gone, and you’ll learn all these things. I too wanted to know how to do it,

01:28:15.000 --> 01:28:18.892
as soon as I got my realization. Sometimes you are a little too keen to know…

01:28:19.000 --> 01:28:21.892
Shri Mataji: But you can tell them how to give first of all protection to your aura.

01:28:22.000 --> 01:28:27.892
This gentleman told Me that his aura was – did get disturbed, it’s true, your aura gets disturbed.

01:28:28.000 --> 01:28:33.892
So you get first of all a method of first of all protecting your auras.

01:28:34.000 --> 01:28:43.892
And how to raise your Kundalini. This method I will teach you today. Alright? After realization. What else?

01:28:44.000 --> 01:28:56.892
Warren: Yes. (A seeker asks one question: “When She talked of saving the creation… (Indistinct) Does She mean that the creation is lost?”)

01:28:57.000 --> 01:29:02.892
Warren: The creation? (Seeker: “She said of saving the creation”.) Yes, I heard the first part. Does She mean…

01:29:03.000 --> 01:29:11.892
(Seeker: “That the creation is lost, or…”- indistinct) (Warren repeats to Shri Mataji:) You spoke of saving the creation. He is asking, do You consider that the creation is lost?

01:29:12.000 --> 01:29:22.892
Shri Mataji: May be, may be lost. It’s not yet lost but may be lost. You see, creation, the epitome of creation is you, is the human beings.

01:29:23.000 --> 01:29:31.892
Alright? If you are not saved, the creation is lost. You are to be saved. And God has to save it, it is His own creation.

01:29:32.000 --> 01:29:42.892
You are His creation. And He has to save it. (To Warren:) I mean, how did a drunkard come in?

01:29:43.000 --> 01:29:48.892
Warren (to a seeker): Yes. (A seeker asks a question) Warren: Say again.

01:29:49.000 --> 01:29:56.892
Seeker: Does She consider the creation something apart from God? Or is the creation also God or what is it?

01:29:57.000 --> 01:30:02.892
(Warren repeats:) Do You consider the creation something apart from God? Or is it also God or what is it?

01:30:03.000 --> 01:30:07.892
Shri Mataji (laughing): Accha, now, you see, this is a subject which I have to deal with, alright?

01:30:08.000 --> 01:30:13.892
What is creation, what is God, how He created you, how we became human beings, it’s a big subject.

01:30:14.000 --> 01:30:20.892
And it’s to be handled sometime and you are to be told all about it. And I cannot just answer it in five minutes.

01:30:21.000 --> 01:30:24.892
But I will, it’s a good question and should come to you.

01:30:25.000 --> 01:30:30.892
But before knowing all these things and details about it, is better you get your light.

01:30:31.000 --> 01:30:35.892
Once you have your light, gradually you start understanding it. Alright?

01:30:36.000 --> 01:30:39.892
Warren: Yes? Seeker: What is the meaning of Sahaja Yoga?

01:30:40.000 --> 01:30:45.892
Shri Mataji: Sahaja. Saha means with – ja means born. Is born with you, spontaneous. Sahaja means spontaneous.

01:30:46.000 --> 01:30:53.892
Whatever is living is spontaneous. You see, whatever happens spontaneously – we don’t understand the word of spontaneous also.

01:30:54.000 --> 01:31:00.892
Means a living, living expression, living manifestation is spontaneous, Sahaja. Is born with you.

01:31:01.000 --> 01:31:06.892
But today Sahaja has gone into the stage called as Maha-Yoga. Means it has become a en-masse.

01:31:07.000 --> 01:31:15.892
It works en-masse. Before it used to work in one person, two persons, you see – like one flower becoming a fruit in the beginning of the tree.

01:31:16.000 --> 01:31:20.892
But today the situation is such that thousands can get realization. It’s Maha-Yoga.

01:31:21.000 --> 01:31:24.892
Sahaja Yoga has matured into Maha-Yoga. Maha means the great.

01:31:25.000 --> 01:31:30.892
(Aside to Warren): I hope he is back – I hope he doesn’t do something to Arneau. Warren: No, the caretaker is outside.
